=head1 DESCRIPTION

Represents the status of the replication of an application to a
location. An application cannot be streamed from a location until it
has finished replicating there.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Location => Str

A location's name. For example, C<us-east-1>. For a complete list of
locations that Amazon GameLift Streams supports, refer to Regions and
quotas
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/gameliftstreams/latest/developerguide/regions-quotas.html)
in the I<Amazon GameLift Streams Developer Guide>.


=head2 Status => Str

The current status of the replication process.



